Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=16}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce aumentou o preco de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:03.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao ta cobrando demais?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:08.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aumenta de novo e eu paro de comprar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual o problema?\NE so um ou dois jornais.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Faz diferenca quando voce\Ncompra todo dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:25.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Voce sabe que nao precisa mais economizar\Nagora que o Arlong saiu da sua vila, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:27.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pode parar de ficar\Nobcecada com dinheiro tambem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e que nao sabe de nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:33.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que tudo acabou,\Neu posso juntar dinheiro pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:38.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao quero ser uma pirata\Npobre que nem consegue se vestir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, calma ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:43.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu to tentando fazer minha\NTabasco Star especial!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um jato disso no olho\Nde qualquer vilao vai–
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai la! So uma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:58.11,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Agua! Agua! Agua!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse e o pomar de tangerinas da Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao vou deixar ninguem encostar nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! Nada vai escapar\Nda minha protecao amorosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E. Obrigada, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:13.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela tem ele na palma da mao...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai la! So uma tangerina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji mao-de-vaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:26.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, tanto faz! Eu to feliz de qualquer jeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:33.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O mundo ta sempre tao caotico.\NMais um golpe em Villa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um panfleto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:15.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao, no minimo, eles se tornaram\Ndemais para nossas filiais lidarem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Correto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo antes de ter uma tripulacao,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:23.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ele derrubou um capitao de filial\Nda Marinha—Morgan Mao-de-Machado—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:26.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e desde entao nao mostrou sinais\Nde que vai parar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Buggy, o Palhaco: 15 milhoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comodoro da Frota Pirata\NDon Krieg: 17 milhoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:37.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pirata Tritao,\NDente-de-Serra Arlong: 20 milhoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:41.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A recompensa media\Nno East Blue e de 3 milhoes de belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:47.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\q2}mas esses grandes piratas—cada um valendo\Nmais de 10 milhoes—foram derrotados!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:52.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E algo sem precedentes no mundo\Numa recompensa comecar em trinta milhoes de belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas tambem nao e um\Nvalor tao excessivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As sementes do mal\Ndevem ser cortadas pela raiz,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,antes que tenham a chance\Nde crescer sem controle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora somos criminosos procurados!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui diz que eu valho 30 milhoes de belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:18.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha! Vou ser visto pelo\Nmundo inteiro! As garotas podem se apaixonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?! Colocaram o\NNarigudo mas me deixaram de fora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde e que voce ta?!\NEu nao te vejo em lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:32.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E so a parte de tras da sua cabeca.\NNao e nada pra se gabar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao fica assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se voce chamar bastante atencao, consegue\Num cartaz mesmo sem ser capitao.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Serio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom, e so continuar se esforcando!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:46.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos logo pra\NGrand Line, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:51.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De novo, voces nao estao\Nentendendo a gravidade disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:54.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A vida de todos nos ta em perigo agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:06:00.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao e hora de ficar de bobeira\Ne relaxando no East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.14,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Trinta milhoes de belly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.79,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O QG da Marinha com certeza vai\Nagir com um numero tao alto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:11.68,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,e vamos ser cercados por\Ncacadores de recompensa fortes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.69,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles vao ser um desafio maior\Ndo que qualquer um que enfrentamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Senhorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Senhorita Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:27.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Senhorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu, Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com certeza e o Usopp\Nde costas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:42.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que voce falou, e verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:48.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Finalmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Voce deu o primeiro passo\Nem direcao ao seu sonho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.89,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Luffy. O homem que\Nvai ser o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.23,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Ate mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:09.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas da proxima vez que nos encontrarmos,\Npodemos ser inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:47.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos finalmente nos\Naproximando da Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:51.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem uma cidade famosa\Nnessa ilha... Loguetown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Loguetown?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E conhecida como a Cidade dos\NComecos e dos Fins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A fama dela a precede.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:05.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, o Rei dos Piratas,\Nnasceu e foi executado nessa cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A cidade onde o Rei\Ndos Piratas morreu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quer ir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim! Eu preciso ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O homem que conseguiu o One Piece—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,tudo o que o mundo tem a oferecer—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,nasceu e morreu la!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem quiser fugir\Nque fuja agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este bastiao de paz nao vai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,tolerar nenhuma fraqueza\Nnesta era de pirataria!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:50.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os fracos e os indefesos nao\Ntem culpa! Eles terao justica!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se o mal persistir nos mares,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:58.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,entao nos, Marinheiros, devemos\Nexpulsa-lo com a maxima forca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Em nome da justica absoluta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:07.27,Note-207-,,0,0,0,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:11.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau! Que cidade enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:16.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse lugar costumava ser cheio de piratas\Na caminho da Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao tem tudo que voce pode precisar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo! Nossa proxima aventura\Nvai ser grande,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,entao eu preciso arranjar equipamentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que eu consigo bons\Ningredientes aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boas mulheres tambem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tambem tem algo que eu quero comprar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah e? E como voce vai fazer isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce ta duro, pelo que eu lembro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo! Eu vou ver\Na plataforma de execucao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:38.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Hein?\N– Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:43.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ver onde\No Rei dos Piratas foi executado!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:46.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera! A gente ainda nao decidiu\Nonde vamos nos encontrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cara, aquele cara...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:55.49,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O Rei dos Piratas\Nnasceu e morreu aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.45,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele pode ter andado\Npor essa mesma rua!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:04.45,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Caramba, isso e caro!\NCaro demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:06.37,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Te emprestar dinheiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.73,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Sem problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.79,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas com os juros, voce vai me dever\N300 por cento do que eu te emprestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:15.01,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso me dar ao luxo de pedir\Nmais emprestado pra ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.20,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,mas eu nao posso entrar na Grand Line\Ncom so uma espada...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.43,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O que eu faco?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.43,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,"Monstro"?! Mas que falta de educacao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:20.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:27.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nosso chefe ta atras das\Ngrades por causa dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:28.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao aprenda com o erro dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa e boa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A gente nao ta satisfeito com as coisas assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:36.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos deixar ele ver\Nseu cadaver quando a gente arrastar ate la!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muito bem. Eu luto com voces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah e mesmo, mocinha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao nos faca rir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que uma garota pode fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:44.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela conseguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e durona, hein!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e incrivel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.03,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nao sei se ela e forte ou fraca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:18.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oculos... Oculos... Oculos...\NCade meus oculos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Meus oculos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei. Ta procurando esses aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,D-Desculpe pelo incomodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que tal esse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! Voce esta maravilhosa, senhorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:34.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que tal esse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esta tao elegante, senhorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E esse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Elementar, senhorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:39.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eletrizante!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Elegiaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai levar todos esses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao, nao quero eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero algo mais despojado.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Volte sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.10,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! Um aperitivo de primeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.61,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! Duas belezas efervescentes\Ncomo champagne de Poinderine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.73,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A cidade inteira ta transbordando\Ndos melhores ingredientes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:05.66,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga, nao consigo decidir\No que escolher primeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.29,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Acabei de encontrar o prato principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.54,Note-207-,,0,0,0,,"Love-Love Pirates"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Demais! Que lugar e esse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo aqui e o sonho de qualquer colecionador!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:25.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tudo aqui pertenceu a piratas\Nque voltaram vivos da Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:28.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses produtos sao especialmente valiosos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:32.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao todos esses itens foram usados\Nem aventuras na Grand Line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Absolutamente correto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui so fazemos negocios com\Nguerreiros do mar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:42.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,entao sera um prazer pessoal\Natender um cavalheiro como voce!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:47.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que me diz? Essa era a arma\Nfavorita do proprio Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?! Do proprio Gold Roger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:51.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que acha, senhor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Me mostra mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigado! Volte sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:04.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde exatamente a gente ta indo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce quebrou meus oculos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:11.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ja disse. Eu vou te\Npagar de volta... de algum jeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao parece ter\Nnenhum dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem algo estranho em voce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-E verdade, eu nao tenho dinheiro, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essas olheiras nos seus olhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce parece que nao\Ncome ha dias!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sua mae ta doente?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:31.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sua esposa te abandonou e te deixou\Ncriando cinco filhos sozinho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Escuta aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao preciso de detalhes!\NSo vem comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A-A Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:51.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se voce trabalhar pra Marinha, nunca\Nmai vai precisar se preocupar com dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nem pensar! Por que eu deveria\Ntrabalhar pra Marinha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:58.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce vai simplesmente sair correndo?!\NEu to tentando te fazer um favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha aqui, voce...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:03.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sargento! Esta na hora do treinamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tchau! Por favor, trabalhe duro, ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sargento?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:11.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Assim eu nao chego a lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que o estilo tres-esfregoes e o melhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixa eu tentar de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce! O que ta fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia! Voce e o Cacador de Piratas Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:38.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que diabos {\i1}voce{\i0}\Nesta aqui limpando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:43.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A inteligencia diz que voce se juntou\Na tripulacao do Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce esta preso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom... e agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que alguem os atacou!\NNao ha rastro do agressor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Pros seus oculos."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.92,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Cara, isso me assustou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:19.61,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Ela se parece\Ndemais com a Kuina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.55,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Sem contar que ela\Ntambem e espadachim...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:26.15,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O mundo e realmente grande,\Nmas duvido que eu va ve-la de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:35.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu gostaria de algumas espadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:40.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah, sim! Bem-vindo!\NFique a vontade pra olhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:43.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nossa loja esta no mercado\Nha 200 anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:48.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho 100.000 belly.\NMe vende duas espadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que...? Duas espadas\Npor 100.000 belly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.47,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga, ele e um pe-rapado.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cinquenta mil por espada so\Nvai te dar umas laminas sem fio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu me viro com qualquer coisa.\NE que nao posso pagar mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:06.83,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai se virar com qualquer coisa?\NHmph! Que amador!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.19,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquela espada na cintura dele!\NSera que e...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:17.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, e-espera. D-D-Deixa eu\Nver essa sua espada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que voce ta tao agitado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-So deixa eu ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esquisito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.04,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,E-E a de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:31.79,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Calma! Essa e sua chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:35.43,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Um amador completo acabou de entrar\Naqui com uma lamina lendaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.72,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce precisa manter a calma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau, essa e uma bela espada\Nque voce tem aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:45.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que me diz? Posso tirar ela\Ndas suas maos por 200.000 belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:48.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso vai te dar um total\Nde 300.000 belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:51.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce vai poder comprar tres\Nlaminas decentes por 100.000 cada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:54.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?! Do que voce ta falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:59.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, ta bom! E-Eu faco por\N250.000... Nao! 300.000!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao, 500.000...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:05.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha. Pode aumentar o preco\No quanto quiser, essa espada nao–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ta bom entao! Eu compro\Npor 650.000 belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:14.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendi! Voce e profissional!\NQue tal 800.000 belly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ola!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce terminou de polir minha Shigure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que bom! Voce esta bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:27.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alguem causou uma confusao\Nno posto da Marinha mais cedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:29.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce sumiu, entao eu fiquei preocupada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:33.03,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ela pode ser tao lerda?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:33.03,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Que bom! Que alivio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas o fato de voce\Nestar aqui, sao e salvo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,significa que voce zombou\Nda minha oferta e fugiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Toma, pega seu dinheiro de volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:45.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso aceitar dinheiro\Nde alguem tao insensivel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alem disso, eu ja comprei\Noculos novos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao me diga que essa espada\Ne {\i1}a{\i0} Wado Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tem{\i0} que ser a Wado Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.30,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Wado...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.05,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao fala! Nao fala!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma bela linha de tempera reta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu acredito que e uma das\Nvinte e uma espadas de Grande Grau!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:14.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ve! Olha isso! Ela vale\Nno minimo 10 milhoes de belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:17.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas como {\i1}voce{\i0} conseguiu\Numa lamina lendaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Voce {\i1}tinha{\i0} que abrir\Nessa boca grande!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou te processar por obstrucao de negocio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-Obstrucao de negocio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa! Eu disse algo errado?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce veio buscar a Shigure, ne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu terminei de polir!\NPega e da o fora daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que voce correu direto naquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Me desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:44.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquela desastrada te salvou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:47.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Serio, uma lamina lendaria\Ne um desperdicio pra um cara que
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}usa ela sem saber seu valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todas as espadas naquele barril\Ncustam 50.000 belly cada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So escolhe duas quaisquer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que ele ta tao bravo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:02.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce deve gostar muito de espadas\Npra querer carregar tres!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me lembra daquele\Ncacador de recompensas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um cacador de recompensas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele e muito conhecido.\NO nome dele e Roronoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ouco esse nome bastante.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:15.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, ele e conhecido por\Ntodo o East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas ele e um demonio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:20.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usar espadas pra cacar\Nrecompensas e imperdoavel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:23.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que o mal ficou tao forte nessa era?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:27.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todos os famosos mestres espadachins\Nsao piratas ou cacadores de recompensa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:31.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eles possuem a maioria\Ndas laminas lendarias do mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E uma pena mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:39.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom, cada um tem suas\Nproprias circunstancias, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:42.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Toda profissao precisa acompanhar\Nos tempos de alguma forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, com minha Shigure,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:47.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,eu vou aprimorar minha esgrima
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:52.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e um dia vou recuperar todas as laminas\Nlendarias dos criminosos do mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:57.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As doze espadas de Grau Supremo,\Nas vinte e uma de Grande Grau,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:00.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e as cinquenta de Bom Grau...\NEu arrisco minha vida por elas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce vai tomar {\i1}essa{\i0} espada tambem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Wado Ichimonji, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer... Nao e que eu queira\Nas laminas lendarias pra mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu so to dizendo que nao quero\Nque criminosos as usem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.65,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa espada...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa espada! Eu acho que e...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia! Kitetsu III!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E a Kitetsu III!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:33.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A antecessora dela, a Kitetsu II,\Ne uma espada de Grande Grau,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e a Kitetsu I antes dela e\Nclassificada como Grau Supremo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Senhor! Essa espada\Ncusta mesmo so 50.000 belly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:46.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incrivel! O grau dessa\Nespada e muito respeitavel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa! Voce {\i1}tem{\i0} que comprar essa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela normalmente sai por um milhao de belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E uma escolha obvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nao! Eu nao posso vender!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:01.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom, claro! Vender isso por 50.000\Nbelly seria muito estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:02.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao, nao e isso...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma espada amaldicoada, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce sabia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao. Eu simplesmente consigo sentir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desde a primeira versao,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:26.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,toda Kitetsu tem sido excepcional,\Nmas cada uma delas carrega uma maldicao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muitos mestres espadachins famosos
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,tiveram mortes tragicas depois\Nde empunhar espadas Kitetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:37.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hoje em dia, voce nao encontra uma unica\Npessoa disposta a usar uma Kitetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:41.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}porque elas vao te tirar desse mundo\Nmesmo se voce usar sem saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:46.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu so quero me livrar dela,\Nmas tenho medo de ser amaldicoado...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:50.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Eu sinto muito! Eu nao fazia ideia\Nque era uma espada tao assustadora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu devia ter cuidado da minha vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:56.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu gostei! Eu levo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,V-Voce e maluco?! Eu nao posso vender!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:03.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se voce morrer por causa dela,\Nvai ser como se eu mesmo tivesse te matado!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:07.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Voce{\i0} que e o maluco! So vende logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:08.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:10.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao vamos fazer assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:13.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Minha sorte, ou a maldicao dessa coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver qual e mais forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:21.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao pode...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:27.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para! Ela e afiada o bastante\Npra arrancar seu braco!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:46.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu levo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:54.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei. Voce pode escolher\Noutra pra mim?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:56.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Claro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:58.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:09.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com uma bainha laqueada de preto...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e o padrao irregular\Nda tempera da lamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:16.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A espada de Bom Grau Yubashiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:21.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Minha loja pode nao ser grande coisa,\Nmas essa e a melhor espada que eu tenho!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:24.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso pagar. Eu ja\Nte disse, nao tenho dinheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:28.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esquece o dinheiro. E eu nao\Npreciso de nada pela Kitetsu tambem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa por ter tentado\Nte enganar antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:34.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Faz tempo que eu nao via os olhos\Nde um bom espadachim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:36.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dizem que a espada\Nescolhe o dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:38.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estarei rezando pela sua boa sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:50.19,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Com certeza me sinto mais\Na vontade com tres espadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.56,0:23:51.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, o que e isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:55.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dificil de acreditar que um mao-de-vaca\Ncomo voce deu o tesouro da familia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:23:58.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um homem nao pode confiar\Nseu sonho a outro?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eu sonho com voce\Ntirando o lixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:02.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:06.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu fiquei tao assustado\Nque ainda nao consigo levantar...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:15.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que e aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:18.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixa eu ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:29.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olhos de Falcao! O que voce ta fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.31,0:24:33.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se acalme. Nao tenho\Nnada contra voce.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.71,0:24:35.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde esta o seu chefe?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.77,0:24:42.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acampado numa ilha dessas...\NQue homem despreocupado.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.51,0:24:48.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-C-Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.01,0:25:01.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-E-E o Olhos de Falcao!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.56,0:25:09.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E ai, Olhos de Falcao.\NIsso e inesperado...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.23,0:25:14.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao to no meu melhor agora...\NVeio procurar briga?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.73,0:25:18.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao tenho intencao de\Nresolver nossas pendencias...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.23,0:25:20.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,agora que voce perdeu o braco esquerdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.21,0:25:24.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu encontrei um pirata interessante...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.86,0:25:27.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e de repente lembrei de uma\Nhistoria que voce costumava contar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:33.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma historia sobre um garoto interessante\Nde uma certa vila pequena...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.26,0:25:35.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao quer dizer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.41,0:25:44.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao voce conseguiu, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.43,0:25:49.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nesse caso, Olhos de Falcao...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.21,0:25:55.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso simplesmente deixar voce ir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.33,0:26:03.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E mesmo, Olhos de Falcao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.19,0:26:07.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso! Bebe! Bebe!\NHoje e dia de comemorar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.89,0:26:09.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao tava de ressaca?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.38,0:26:11.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Relaxa! E uma bebida de comemoracao!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.87,0:26:13.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamo la! Vamo la!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.36,0:26:16.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So vira de uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.57,0:26:21.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao e nada mal!\NVamos beber! Vamos beber!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:22.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.10,0:26:23.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas, espera! Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.35,0:26:26.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce disse que tava passando mal\Nporque bebeu demais antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.90,0:26:30.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu tonto! Como eu {\i1}nao{\i0} vou beber\Nnum dia alegre como hoje!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.46,0:26:31.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O sol ainda ta alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.84,0:26:33.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Relaxa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.29,0:26:35.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer uma festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.99,0:26:44.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! O Luffy agora e um procurado!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.02,0:26:45.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom pra ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:48.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sabia que essa vila pode\Ndar um grande pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.95,0:26:50.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso seria otimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:53.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quietos, seus cabecas-duras!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.27,0:26:54.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Senhor prefeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.59,0:26:58.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que tem de bom num criminoso\Nvir da nossa vila?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:27:00.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um brinde!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.97,0:27:05.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sinceramente! Cada um deles...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.03,0:27:10.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual e, prefeito!\NO Luffy parece tao feliz aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.48,0:27:12.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pirata e pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.69,0:27:17.32,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ser o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.73,0:27:22.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Claro, mas e o sonho dele.\NIsso te preocupa?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.53,0:27:27.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O sonho dele... ou destino?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=17}===============================DIALOGUE============================
